    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, maintained to the highest standards of automotive preservation. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish with zero imperfections, swirl marks, or rock chips, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in a showroom state; the premium leather upholstery is supple with no bolster wear, the carpets are spotless, and the interior still carries a faint factory-new scent. Every electronic feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is in peak condition, backed by a complete, documented service history and a recent comprehensive inspection. The engine bay is clean enough to eat off of, and the undercarriage shows no signs of road salt or wear. It has been exclusively garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment and has never seen rain or snow. This is a turn-key opportunity for a collector or enthusiast seeking a vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line.",
